	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" /><a href="http://nesicide.com/downloads/setup.msi" class="postlink">V1.002 (setup.msi)</a>
<br />Added Find-in-Files dockable window.  Search output goes to output dockable window and from there it can be clicked on to bring up the relevant file/line.  (Typical IDE find-in-files functionality.)
<br />
<br />Added current-file search widget to toolbar.  (Search-as-you-type, forward or backward, case sensitive or not, regular expression or plaintext.  Typical IDE search bar functionality.)
<br />
<br />Fixed SVG icon problems--moved to PNG.  (Thanks Memblers!)
<br />
<br />Project now accepts any file types and only passes .c or .s files to compiler.
<br />
<br />Clicking on marker start/end cells in the Execution Visualizer will show that location in the Assemby Inspector or in the Code Editor if the appropriate source file is open.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


