		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" /><a href="http://nesicide.com/downloads/setup.msi" class="postlink">V1.003 (setup.msi)</a>
<br />
<br />Added persistence to options for search widget in toolbar.
<br />
<br />Fixed source navigator toolbar widget so symbol selector works--opens file where symbol is found and goes to that line.
<br />
<br />Added Ctrl+F hotkey for search toolbar activation, and Ctrl+Shift+F hotkey for Find-in-Files dialog activation.

		

